WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:08.880
[Amit Varma]: Many years ago, I was hanging out with a friend of mine in an industrial park.

00:00:08.880 --> 00:00:13.200
[Amit Varma]: His name is Narendra and he wasn't, at that time, the Prime Minister of India.

00:00:13.200 --> 00:00:17.320
[Amit Varma]: So we were just shooting the breeze, talking about girls and cars and all the books we'd

00:00:17.320 --> 00:00:21.520
[Amit Varma]: read, I mean all the books I'd read because he isn't much of a reader, when suddenly it

00:00:21.520 --> 00:00:22.720
[Amit Varma]: started raining.

00:00:22.720 --> 00:00:27.080
[Amit Varma]: I love the rain and this change in weather put me in a mellow mood.

00:00:27.080 --> 00:00:28.080
[Amit Varma]: Isn't this lovely?

00:00:28.080 --> 00:00:29.440
[Unknown]: I asked Narendra.

00:00:29.440 --> 00:00:35.480
[Unknown]: Yes, it's very romantic, he said as he reached out and touched my arm gently.

00:00:35.480 --> 00:00:39.200
[Unknown]: I could really do with some chai and pakoras right now.

00:00:39.200 --> 00:00:43.740
[Amit Varma]: I can organise the chai, I replied, but where will we get pakoras from over here?

00:00:43.740 --> 00:00:45.560
[Amit Varma]: No one here sells pakoras.

00:00:45.560 --> 00:00:48.400
[Amit Varma]: When he heard that, Narendra got very serious.

00:00:48.400 --> 00:00:51.760
[Unknown]: He thundered, No one here sells pakoras?

00:00:51.760 --> 00:00:53.680
[Unknown]: That is preposterous.

00:00:53.680 --> 00:00:55.280
[Unknown]: This must change.

00:00:55.280 --> 00:01:00.640
[Unknown]: I will change it.

